UNICEF aims to achieve this through Systems Strengthening And Institution Building. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: Outcome 6: By 2014, MOSA is further developed to implement and monitor the National Plan of Action for Child Protection. Together with humanitarian partnerships, this will ensure that children who are at risk of, or subject to, all forms of violence, exploitation, and abuse, benefit from improved services.
